   <Reference>Hastie, A.R., Kerr, A.C., Pearce, J.A., Mitchell, S.F., 2007, Classification of Altered Volcanic Island Arc Rocks using Immobile Trace Elements: Development of the Th-Co Discrimination Diagram.  Journal of Petrology, v. 48, p. 2341-2357.</Reference>
